<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2935] Problem while extracting font from PDFontSetting (used in PDExtendedGraphicsState)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2935</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PDFontSetting.getFont() :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; PDFont getFont() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException
    {
        PDFont retval = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
        COSBase font = fontSetting.get( 0 );
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;( font &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; COSDictionary )
        {
            retval = PDFontFactory.createFont( (COSDictionary)font );
        }
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; retval;
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If font is referenced as indirect object this method returns null, while font is valid and present in document. &lt;br/&gt;
Example :&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;10 0 obj
&amp;lt;&amp;lt;
/Font [13 0 R 60000]
/Type /ExtGState
&amp;gt;&amp;gt;
endobj

13 0 obj
&amp;lt;&amp;lt;
/BaseFont /ASJKFO+Arial-BoldMT
/Encoding /WinAnsiEncoding
/FirstChar 65
/FontDescriptor 16 0 R
/LastChar 65
/Subtype /TrueType
/Type /Font
/Widths [722]
&amp;gt;&amp;gt;
endobj
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
